    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable car that still feels fresh and well-loved, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This unit excels mechanically, with the dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response up to the 8,400 RPM limit. The M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) are fully operational, maintaining the car's celebrated handling characteristics. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a rod bearing service and replacement of the throttle actuators, mitigating common S65 failure points. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust and the subframe is structurally sound. An excellent opportunity for an enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound platform optimized for performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Runs well. Regular maintenance performed. Clean interior. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
