    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal, perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that has been treated with care. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, though I want to be upfront about a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, two-inch scratch near the rear wheel well that has been professionally touched up. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all instrument clusters and infotainment features fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in solid health. It features a complete service history, with the most recent work including a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. The tires are matching all-seasons with plenty of tread depth left for several seasons of driving. This is a well-sorted car that drives as good as it looks, offering a refined experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
